**`async apply_webhook_event(self, payload: WebhookPayload) -> UpdateResult`:**

Validates `payload.project_id > 0`. Raise `ValueError` if not.

Authoritative flow:
1. `if not self._store.is_project_tracked(payload.project_id)`: log DEBUG `webhook_project_not_tracked`. Return `UpdateResult(..., applied=False, reason="project_not_tracked")`.
2. `state = await self._store.get_project_state(payload.project_id)`. If `None`: log WARNING. Return `UpdateResult(..., applied=False, reason="no_state_for_project")`.
