7. `await self._store.update_entity(payload.project_id, entity_type, entity)`.
8. Extract new relationships for updated entity. Call `update_index_for_entity()`. Update `state.relationship_index`.
9. Re-run consistency check and update `state.metadata.health`.
10. `state.metadata.last_updated_at = datetime.now(timezone.utc)`.
11. Log INFO: `webhook_entity_updated` with `project_id`, `entity_type`, `entity_id`.
12. Return `UpdateResult(..., applied=True, reason="applied")`.

